{"tid":1033139,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"微軟員工促公司棄37億美國軍隊合約","createTime":"2019-02-23T01:40:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-23T12:40:25.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"53456974689e53380cfda31bcde297d5f2f28e05","tid":1033139,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T01:40:04.000Z","msg":"路透引述3名微軟員工稱，有微軟員工組織運動，促請公司放棄美國國防授予的4.8億美元(37.44億港元)合約，因為有關合約全部涉及開發武器技術。<br />\n<br />\n微軟去年11月取得軍方的供應合約，要求公司提供最少2500個虛擬實景頭盔的樣版。該款頭盔讓用者可以肉眼看到按照電子數據而展示的畫面。<br />\n<br />\n根據有微軟員工在Twitter發表的致管理層函件，員工不希望開發與戰爭有關科技，而且要求公司容許他們對開發的產品用途有話語權，包括發展一個可讓其開發科技用於合宜用途，並且有外間機構監督有關情況。<br />\n<br />\n微軟與軍方拒評上述消息。微軟總裁Brad Smith去年10月公開表示，將繼續協助美國軍方。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2065511\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F2065511&d=gMg1FBwAZA1XbJy1Uvmn1NTdZGttzgfhyqIgu1GDYj0%3D&h=beac863a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2065511</a>"},{"pid":"942c9280c1407330e57c845af3866693215226d4","tid":1033139,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T02:02:31.000Z","msg":"IRON MAN<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c28b2ff5d81aa929cf2d7d0e43c00cfd6f738c25","tid":1033139,"uid":141151,"like":60,"dislike":1,"score":59,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T02:02:50.000Z","msg":"左膠到<br />\n<br />\n美軍白紙黑字同你合作你唔幫<br />\n贏国濫用技術打壓人民你就幫到足幻想有市場"},{"pid":"bc11272df8bf33df00de29d5ef3606fc6453664e","tid":1033139,"uid":121146,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T02:04:53.000Z","msg":"左膠禍國"},{"pid":"74eb3e4d91b0473e59c07554a27da0d6ae4c5085","tid":1033139,"uid":52459,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T02:11:24.000Z","msg":"打工仔叫腦細唔好做生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgm