nail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqZzEHmz.png&h=1825cf65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n李舜是李飛飛的父親，成都育才小學九屆學生。李飛飛父親的父親是四川人，參加革命去了延安，解放戰爭南下，建國初期在川北行署，是胡耀邦部下，後在四川省李井泉領導之下，任瀘州專員。算是紅一代。<br />\n<br />\n 1992年李舜夫婦帶著16歲的李飛飛，飛往了美國，追求自己的工程師和科學家之夢。在新澤西州的一個小鎮上，一個成了相機修理工，一個成了收銀員&hellip;&hellip;。<br />\n<br />\n    據紅二代申再望（李井泉副委員長五子）說：我的養母申國藩是成都育才小學校長，幾百學生都是乾部子弟，清一色紅二代。育才校友群有幾百人，李舜常在群內發文。育才小學始建於山西臨汾，賀鵬飛（賀龍元帥之子）、李黎風（李井泉副委員長長子）等是第一屆學生。顯然，李飛飛身上有紅色基因，有中國情結。<br />\n是一個&ldquo;中、西結合&rdquo;的紅三代。<br />\n<br />\n2017.12.23於順德<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.weibo.com/ttarticle/p/show?id=2313501000014187806212689047\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.weibo.com%2Fttarticle%2Fp%2Fshow%3Fid%3D2313501000014187806212689047&d=gMg1FBwAZA1XbJy1Uvmn1NTdZGttzgfhyqIgu1GDYj0%3D&h=caf03f6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.weibo.com/ttarticle/p/show?id=2313501000014187806212689047</a><br />\n0<br />\n0"},{"pid":"2758051362aa3551897b7f29dc9f00a4cbd0f4d1","tid":1033139,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T08:33:04.000Z","msg":"google 都幾撚戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2734e9c152222ae07aa1190b21f8b301d0a467af","tid":1033139,"uid":138593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2758051362aa3551897b7f29dc9f00a4cbd0f4d1","tid":1033139,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T08:33:04.000Z","msg":"google 都幾撚戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T08:41:19.000Z","msg":"畀蝻加蝗破壞哂"},{"pid":"c5b33101c55b7dd3175